I"Åò<p>In this post, I tell you about <em>how to create a Chamfer through Solidworks VBA Macros</em> in a sketch.</p>

<p>This post is an extension of <strong><a href="/solidworks-macros/create-corner-rectangle">Sketch - Create Corner Rectangle</a></strong> post.</p>

