<p>Please see below video how visually we can create <em>a Chamfer</em> from <strong>Solidworks VBA macro</strong>.</p>

<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HobbXAv9zMI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

